last_episode_to_air.name: Awakening
last_episode_to_air.overview: Sindhu and Diana woke up in a room they did not recognize. The house belongs to Diego and Sharon, a married couple whose relationship was cold after the death of their baby. Because no one ever came to see Sindhu and Diana, Diana was certain that they were being kidnapped.

name: Temaram
overview: The smart person who handled Sharon decided to come home. Who exactly Shindu and Diana were revealed to be.
